{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_017kaZ1F6EX7A3dbxTk4Lf5J","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the improvement plan and the current state of the code. Let me implement the 4 changes described in the plan:\n\n1. **Fix A**: Breadcrumb filter in `passesHardFilters` - Add a filter for lines containing 2+ forward-slash characters\n2. **Fix B**: Mid-word casing transition in `isLikelyGarbled` - Add detection for single words with internal lowercase-to-uppercase transitions\n3. **Fix C**: Metadata continuation suppression in `buildCandidates` - Skip short ALL_CAPS fragments after metadata lines\n4. **Fix D**: OCR-resilient DLA metadata pattern in `METADATA_PATTERNS`\n \nImplementing the code changes... Adding metadata pattern detection...","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":17569,"cache_read_input_tokens":19683,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":17569},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6e03cb61-049b-40c5-8a90-8c6b34cd394a","uuid":"4aceea2d-027d-43b0-ab6e-35533ee6d058"}
