{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01HNMiX19qsCBPo3doPVWkjc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 32 tests pass. Here's a summary of the 4 changes made to `title-extractor.ts`:\n\n1. **`METADATA_PATTERNS`** — Added two OCR-resilient DLA patterns: `/^DLA\\s+\\S+\\s+OSOB/i` and `/^DLA\\s+[^a-zA-Z0-9\\s]\\s/i`. Fixes `DLA & OSOB` (OCR-corrupted `DLA 4 OSÓB`) being misclassified as a recipe title.\n\n2. **`isLikelyGarbled`** — Added check for single words with internal lowercase→uppercase transitions (e.g., `UuIw`, `aBC`). OCR noise pattern that never appears in natural language.\n\n3. **`passesHardFilters`** — Added breadcrumb filter: lines with 2+ slashes (e.g., `/ Jesien / Zupy`) are navigation breadcrumbs, not titles. Single-slash lines like `TITLE FIRST PART / SECOND PART` are unaffected.\n\n4. **`buildCandidates`** — Added metadata continuation suppression: short ALL_CAPS fragments (≤2 words, ≤15 chars) immediately following a metadata line are skipped. Fixes `BALLS` after `MAKES 25 LABANEH` leaking into candidates and eliminating `LABANEH BALLS WITH NIGELLA SEEDS` via dedup."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":283,"cache_read_input_tokens":48707,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":283},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6e03cb61-049b-40c5-8a90-8c6b34cd394a","uuid":"584ca50b-3120-4029-af88-476490a1e8b4"}
